onopol beschreibt, oder dem der »Differenzierten Schule« als Darstellung der Folgen bisheriger Praxis - wird die Tragfähigkeit des Instruments diskutiert.  afunded by ÖFG (?)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aSchool buildings. 4aAltbaumodernisierung. 4aArchitektur. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aGebäudebestand. 4aTransition Theory. 7aARCHITECTURE / Urban & Land Use Planning.2bisacsh  aArchitecture.  aBuilding Stock.  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aTransition Theory.2 aÖFG (?)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2020z9783110704679oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839442944zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839442944423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839442944.jpg  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020